aight ahead, because I sure couldn't move the camera at all.-I've played for 2 hours, already unlocked half the game content-what I haven't unlocked consists of 2 other cars and three rallys comprising of locations and stages that I have already played, but this time with the abritrary ""this is where the computer car would be"" icon that scrolls along a bar at the top of the screen moving a bit faster-----------doesn't play the playstation startup tune when the game is first loading (unforgivable oversight)-doesn't fetch the newspaper for you-It's not 1998 anymore-I'm getting old-you're getting old-you used to be beautiful-I'm just not feeling it anymore, alright?"
